{"tid":1226310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"父親節做孝子, 帶身邊人重回正軌, 唔好放棄任何香港人","createTime":"2019-06-15T10:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T19:06:27.000Z","uid":19817,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cb430ccb474f65ac28c6e2811c481d97956319c6","tid":1226310,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T10:58:32.000Z","msg":"我想借呢個高質POST講少少野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1222840/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1222840/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P3L8BPE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP3L8BPE.png&h=9b3bfcf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽完好多母親發起好多令人心痛流淚既說話,<br />\n<br />\n作為人個男性, 或者將來作為一個父親聽到都忍唔住會突然吹沙入眼,<br />\n<br />\n事實上香港有好多上一代都由唔同地方落黎香港落地生根, 佢地生活好忙, 要養家, 要休息.<br />\n<br />\n佢地冇時間去理會好多社會上發生既野, 亦未必會真係直接關佢地事, 佢地大部分都想我地下一代好, 但無奈佢地受到各樣媒體, APP, 農場文, 飛機文誤導, 會令到你十分失望, 沮喪, 煩厭.<br />\n<br />\n而我亦都係其中一個, 由細到大幼稚園到大學都教你要做一個良好公民, 人權與法治, 明辯是非.呢D野扎根左係我地既心入面, 係時侯到我地將呢D野教番出去, 我知道係好難好難, 我知道你會諗屋企唔應該因為政治而嘈, 但正因為我地一路咁諗先令到佢地今日會咁樣, 冰封三呎非一日之寒, 係時候到我地將我地學既野學以所用教番佢地<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">你可能會話 哂9氣喇 佢地點都唔化架喇!   留黎教仔好過</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">錯!!你呢家唔教番上一代, 有機會留傳俾下一代咩?, 定係你仲會係一個惡劣既環境下生你既下一代?  我真係好羡慕有D人既屋企係支持, 但羡慕係冇用, 不如靠自己喇! 唔好再話冇可能, 所有野一開頭都係冇可能架!!!  <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">100萬人出黎</span>都俾人話過冇可能架!!!</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">父親節一齊做孝子既本份, 做個香港人既本份<br />\n唔好放棄任何身邊人!<br />\n香港見!!!</span></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"64729ab897824d74dd2acc71c0f2a1750c314b3b","tid":1226310,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2deabda74f2c7e65f25ad3f4d164d0f1b97494","tid":1226310,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a442b8114987e5aee8b4857363234f08eed4c63c","tid":1226310,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:29:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d66de953d050f4edb5c88a2c45cf07ba6f5ad0","tid":1226310,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3e28cb7630193ee7c2da8d5ae108eb31356922","tid":1226310,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}